<div class="title">The Unimaginable Terror of Enlightenment</div>
<div class="substance">Pharmahusaca (Syrian Rue & DMT) & Mushrooms - Panaeolus cyanescens</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=Sam&Exact=1">Sam</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; Sam. "The Unimaginable Terror of Enlightenment: An Experience with Pharmahusaca (Syrian Rue & DMT) & Mushrooms - Panaeolus cyanescens (exp68768)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Sep 2, 2008. erowid.org/exp/68768</div>

<br/>



